506
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:49,540
(Complaining)

507
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,720
You put it on wrong.

508
00:13:53,780 --> 00:13:55,380
(Totally)

509
00:13:55,460 --> 00:13:56,540
(Can't stop laughing.)

510
00:13:56,620 --> 00:13:57,900
(Caught up in the fun)

511
00:14:02,360 --> 00:14:03,000
How much time left?

512
00:14:03,100 --> 00:14:03,800
(Two minutes left)

513
00:14:03,800 --> 00:14:04,560
Oh, that's okay.

514
00:14:04,560 --> 00:14:05,840
T-shirts are faster.

515
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:07,160
Right?

516
00:14:07,160 --> 00:14:07,720
Yeah.

517
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:10,320
But it should get harder later, right?

518
00:14:12,620 --> 00:14:15,140
(Speed is blazing)

519
00:14:15,260 --> 00:14:16,040
(Keeping low "altitude")

520
00:14:16,040 --> 00:14:18,120
(Stronger "tremor" in the legs)
Stop shaking your legs.

521
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:19,960
Oh no, he's shaking. I'll be shaking too.

522
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,000
Of course you will.

523
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,140
(Anxious)

524
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,840
Put it all together...

525
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:26,540
(Seems like it's meant to be.)

526
00:14:29,220 --> 00:14:31,940
(Kissing your public image goodbye.)

527
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:38,600
How many have we done?

528
00:14:44,860 --> 00:14:45,780
(Only a few T-shirts left)

529
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:47,000
Good.

530
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:48,880
It's getting kinda warm.

531
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:49,680
(Fired up)
Hurry!

532
00:14:49,700 --> 00:14:50,940
(Rejected)

533
00:14:51,520 --> 00:14:52,720
I'm falling down.

534
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:53,240
That's okay.

535
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:54,480
Only one left. Hurry.

536
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:57,820
(T-shirts cleared)

537
00:14:58,720 --> 00:14:59,840
They're so fast.

538
00:15:00,640 --> 00:15:01,280
We can do that.

539
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:04,400
How much time left?

540
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:05,600
No, keep going.

541
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:07,640
Ten? How many?

542
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:08,660
(15 seconds left)

543
00:15:08,740 --> 00:15:10,460
(Highly focused)

544
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:11,800
No need.

545
00:15:11,800 --> 00:15:12,440
That's it.

546
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:13,590
(Not enough time for another shirt)
One more.

547
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:14,200
I'm going down.

548
00:15:18,100 --> 00:15:21,460
(Yang turns into the Michelin Man)

549
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:27,040
The Michelin Man.

550
00:15:28,260 --> 00:15:29,420
(Scoring the fourth group)

551
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:30,280
Come on.

552
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:33,440
Take them off.

553
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:34,720
One.

554
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:36,140
(1 point)

555
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:37,280
Two.

556
00:15:37,280 --> 00:15:38,060
(2 points)

557
00:15:38,160 --> 00:15:38,720
Three.

558
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:39,140
(3 points)

559
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:39,960
Four.

560
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:40,660
(4 points)

561
00:15:40,700 --> 00:15:42,060
(All eyes on them)

562
00:15:42,160 --> 00:15:42,840
Five.

563
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:43,620
(5 points)

564
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:44,920
(6 points)
Six.

565
00:15:45,760 --> 00:15:46,320
Seven.

566
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:47,220
(7 points)

567
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:48,000
Eight.

568
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:48,340
(8 points)

569
00:15:48,380 --> 00:15:49,300
(Victory in sight)

570
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:50,340
(9 points)
Nine.

571
00:15:50,340 --> 00:15:52,300
(Got this in the bag.)

572
00:15:52,760 --> 00:15:53,360
Ten.

573
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:55,880
Eleven.

574
00:15:55,880 --> 00:15:56,360
(11 points)

575
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:57,200
Twelve?

576
00:15:58,240 --> 00:15:59,040
(12 points)
Twelve.

577
00:15:59,740 --> 00:16:00,660
(T-shirt "killer")

578
00:16:00,700 --> 00:16:03,420
(Yang Tianyu & Wu Yihan: 12 T-shirts,
0 shirts, 12 points, currently 1st place)

579
00:16:07,260 --> 00:16:08,980
