In what way?

864
00:26:07,900 --> 00:26:08,560
(Grab her.)

865
00:26:08,560 --> 00:26:10,760
The "Smart Beauty" and the "Goofy Hunk."

866
00:26:10,760 --> 00:26:12,040
(Laughs)
No, you're smart too.

867
00:26:12,800 --> 00:26:14,820
(Staring)
Your analysis was spot on.

868
00:26:16,080 --> 00:26:16,880
That's sweet.

869
00:26:17,480 --> 00:26:18,680
I enjoy talking to you.

870
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:20,200
Yeah, me too.

871
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:21,120
Let's go chat more.

872
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:22,480
To the kitchen.

873
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:23,040
Hey.

874
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:24,600
Why are we

875
00:26:24,600 --> 00:26:25,400
out of sync today?

876
00:26:26,360 --> 00:26:27,640
Maybe we're just bad at games.

877
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:29,320
But we won on day one.

878
00:26:29,660 --> 00:26:32,260
(Can't take her eyes off him.)

879
00:26:32,280 --> 00:26:33,800
Because we barely knew each other?

880
00:26:33,800 --> 00:26:34,400
(Tough question)

881
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:35,240
So, less chemistry,

882
00:26:35,240 --> 00:26:36,280
more luck, I guess?

883
00:26:36,600 --> 00:26:37,480
Now we know each other.

884
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:38,640
On day one, I carried us.

885
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:39,720
I tried so hard.

886
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:40,640
Hey, I tried too.

887
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:41,640
Of course, you did.

888
00:26:41,640 --> 00:26:42,320
Yeah.

889
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:43,880
Honestly, you're not meant for

890
00:26:44,320 --> 00:26:45,480
this kind of "manual labor."

891
00:26:45,620 --> 00:26:46,260
(Trust me on this.)

892
00:26:48,480 --> 00:26:49,400
I want one too.

893
00:26:49,620 --> 00:26:50,700
(Sulking)

894
00:26:52,040 --> 00:26:54,560
Let me handle this kind thing from now on.

895
00:26:54,560 --> 00:26:55,120
(So sweet)

896
00:26:55,120 --> 00:26:55,600
Alright then.

897
00:26:55,600 --> 00:26:57,160
Next time there's a task

898
00:26:57,160 --> 00:26:58,680
like buttoning,

899
00:26:59,080 --> 00:27:01,280
or fighting for something,

900
00:27:01,640 --> 00:27:02,280
that's my job.

901
00:27:02,520 --> 00:27:03,400
Deal.

902
00:27:03,400 --> 00:27:04,760
You're good at making up for me.

903
00:27:04,760 --> 00:27:05,740
(Pulls)

904
00:27:10,460 --> 00:27:11,780
(Between shared breaths,)

905
00:27:11,780 --> 00:27:15,860
(love takes a clearer shape.)

906
00:27:16,350 --> 00:27:18,650
(Watch Live and Love with us)
♪Take a look at my girlfriend♪

907
00:27:18,950 --> 00:27:20,640
(on Thu. 12 PM.)
♪She's the only one I've got♪

908
